116
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:40,830
Prestasi militernya diperoleh
di medan perang.

117
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:43,240
Kasus yang asli
promosi melalui kredit.

118
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,040
Sekarang...

119
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,480
Sekarang,

120
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,390
