453
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:36,690
Kabupaten Wei kami relatif beruntung.

454
00:17:36,690 --> 00:17:38,170
Di kota-kota yang paling parah terkena dampaknya,

455
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,350
